								<p class="website"><a href="http://www.akzonobel.com/news/information_former_ici/" class="url"><b>www.akzonobel.com</b></a></p>
								<p class="industry field"><b>INDUSTRY:</b> Manufacturing</p>
								<p class="business field"><b>BUSINESS:</b> Specialty products and paints with over 50,000 products and ingredients developed for a wide range of consumer and industrial markets.</p>
								<p class="scope field"><b>SCOPE & SIZE:</b> ICI employs over 35,000 people worldwide and had £5.8 billion in 2003 revenue (US $11 billion).</p>
							</div>
							<div class="swiper-slide">
								<img src="https://q-website-images.s3.amazonaws.com/www/image/logo/capital-one-white.svg" width="141" height="51" class="logo">
								<p class="size field"><b>BUSINESS CHALLENGE:</b> Centralized view of network security with focus on ensuring safety of both internal and outsourced infrastructure.</p>
								<p class="size field"><b>OPERATIONAL HURDLE:</b> Giant distributed global business needed to ensure security of its mostly outsourced network infrastructure. Auditing the security of network and hosts on demand when most of IT was outsourced globally to 3rd party suppliers.</p>
								<p class="size field"><b>SOLUTION:</b> Used a 3rd party web service from Qualys to automatically find vulnerabilities in outsourced IT and provide remediation management to each supplier.</p>
