					<p class="why"><b>Why Imperial Chemical Industries chose Qualys:</b></p>
					<ul class="reasons">
						<li class="reason">Qualys worldwide deployment completed within hours.</li>
						<li class="reason">ICI can now scan its entire global infrastructure for vulnerabilities at least once a week.</li>
						<li class="reason">Automated security audits and remediation workflow across the enterprise.</li>
